{"tid":1654773,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[Twitter戰線] 10.13炸彈 要點同外媒講","createTime":"2019-10-14T17:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T01:14:38.000Z","uid":329309,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33dc1ec4d91cf03a307bbc5e4478bdbb99acb09d","tid":1654773,"uid":329309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:52:59.000Z","msg":"外國媒體報導入面已經勁多5毛煲大緊手足放炸彈，話我地係恐怖分子呀，大家快d開工！<br />\n<br />\n比咗幾個方向大家選擇<br />\n1. 唔知邊個放炸彈，唔排除黑警/中共特工放，抹黑示威者。香港自從親共暴徒67暴徒後冇人放炸彈，正常香港人唔識整。<br />\nIt is not known who made the bomb, but it cannot be ruled out that the real terrorists could be CCP agents as smear tactics. It is unlikely that HK protesters have the knowledge and skills to make bomb, as bombs are not seen in HK after 1967 riot by pro-communists.<br />\n<br />\n2. 傳言新疆恐襲係中共自編自導自演，目的係提供理據興建大量再教育營，用作今日大量囚禁穆斯林。 同樣情況可能正在香港上演，如新疆嶺。<br />\nRumours say the Xinjiang bombs terrorists were CCP agents, to pave way for building massive re-education camps for #Uyghurs today to tackle terrorism. It could be similar tactics employed in HK too.<br />\n<br />\n3. 中國一早預言香港示威者係恐怖分子，今次可能係佢地自編自導自演嫁禍示威者，附link: <br />\nChina had prophesized terrorists attack in HK in Aug and Sep. Now this could be them fulfilling their own play, to smear HK protesters. Links below:<br />\n國務院<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-china-statement/chinas-hong-kong-office-condemns-near-terrorist-acts-at-hong-kong-airport-idUSKCN1V40AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-china-statement%2Fchinas-hong-kong-office-condemns-near-terrorist-acts-at-hong-kong-airport-idUSKCN1V40AD&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm98RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=22495463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-china-statement%2Fchinas-hong-kong-office-condemns-near-terrorist-acts-at-hong-kong-airport-idUSKCN1V40AD&h=2b2b5823\" data-auto-link target=\"